                "webUrl": "https://www.theguardian.com/business/commentisfree/article/2024/aug/24/gina-rineharts-latest-grab-bag-of-opinions-is-more-proof-billionaires-are-no-smarter-than-the-rest-of-us",
                "apiUrl": "https://content.guardianapis.com/business/commentisfree/article/2024/aug/24/gina-rineharts-latest-grab-bag-of-opinions-is-more-proof-billionaires-are-no-smarter-than-the-rest-of-us",
