                "webTitle": "Western Sydney has long been Labor ground. But is anger over Gaza making voters think twice?",
                "webUrl": "https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/article/2024/aug/24/western-sydney-has-long-been-labor-ground-but-is-anger-over-gaza-making-voters-think-twice",
                "apiUrl": "https://content.guardianapis.com/australia-news/article/2024/aug/24/western-sydney-has-long-been-labor-ground-but-is-anger-over-gaza-making-voters-think-twice",
