                "webTitle": "Emily Wurramara on surviving a house fire: ‘When I had nothing, I had everything’",
                "webUrl": "https://www.theguardian.com/music/article/2024/aug/24/emily-wurramara-artist-interview-playlist-music",
                "apiUrl": "https://content.guardianapis.com/music/article/2024/aug/24/emily-wurramara-artist-interview-playlist-music",
