                "webUrl": "https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/article/2024/aug/24/agl-breached-rules-16000-times-in-wrongly-taking-welfare-money-from-hundreds-of-people-court-rules",
                "apiUrl": "https://content.guardianapis.com/australia-news/article/2024/aug/24/agl-breached-rules-16000-times-in-wrongly-taking-welfare-money-from-hundreds-of-people-court-rules",
